CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 25, 2011

[Cite as 01/25/2011 Case Announcements #2, 2011-Ohio-291.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2002-1380. Disciplinary Counsel v. Brown.

This cause came on for further consideration upon relator’s filing of a motion to appear and show cause.

Upon consideration thereof, relator’s motion is denied.
